OL,3,CRobbery mastermind who fled UK jailed
OL,4,Cfor PC's murder
OL,6,FThe mastermind of an armed robbery
OL,7,Fduring which a police officer was shot
OL,8,Fdead will spend the rest of his life
OL,9,Fin prison after being jailed for her
OL,10,Fmurder.
OL,12,FPiran Ditta Khan, now 75, fled the UK
OL,13,Fafter PC Sharon Beshenivsky's death in
OL,14,FBradford in 2005.
OL,16,FHe was extradited from Pakistan in
OL,17,FApril last year and was found guilty
OL,18,Fof murder following a trial at Leeds
OL,19,FCrown Court last month.
