OL,6,FKhan, who was 57 at the time of
OL,7,Fincident, was the last of seven men to
OL,8,Fface justice.
OL,10,FHe was given a life sentence on
OL,11,FFriday, with a minimum term of 40
OL,12,Fyears. The number of days he has spent
OL,13,Fin custody since his arrest will be
OL,14,Fdeducted from the term.
OL,16,FJudge Mr Justice Hillard told him: "No
OL,17,Fsentence I pass can put right what you
OL,18,Fhave done."
OL,20,FHe added: "You will inevitably spend
OL,21,Fthe rest of your life in custody."
