OL,6,FPC Beshenivsky, a 38-year-old mother-
OL,7,Fof-three, was shot dead after
OL,8,Fresponding to reports of a raid at
OL,9,FUniversal Express travel agents on
OL,10,FMorley Street, Bradford, on 18
OL,11,FNovember 2005 ` the day her daughter
OL,12,FLydia turned four.
OL,14,FHer colleague PC Teresa Milburn was
OL,15,Falso shot but survived.
OL,17,F, or that weapons were going to be
OL,18,Fused.
