OL,3,CRobbery mastermind who fled UK jailed
OL,4,Cfor PC's murder
OL,6,FHe claimed an associate had merely
OL,7,Foffered to get back #12,000 owed to
OL,8,Fhim by the owner of the travel agents.
OL,10,FBut prosecutors said Khan played a
OL,11,F"pivotal" role in planning the raid
OL,12,Fand gave instructions to the others.
OL,14,F, but the prosecution said he was as
OL,15,Fguilty "as surely as if he had pulled
OL,16,Fthe trigger himself".
OL,18,FRobert Smith KC, prosecuting, told the
OL,19,Fsentencing hearing the robbery
OL,20,Finvolved "a substantial degree of
OL,21,Funnecessary violence".
