OL,6,FMr Smith said: "The defendant was
OL,7,Fpresent, waiting nearby and was
OL,8,Finstrumental in giving instructions to
OL,9,Fenter the premises and carrying out
OL,10,Fthe intended robbery.
OL,12,F"In doing so, he knew they would be
OL,13,Fcarrying the weapons in question,
OL,14,Floaded with ammunition and he shared
OL,15,Fthe common intention with them to
OL,16,Fshoot any person who sought to
OL,17,Fobstruct them and get their arrest."
OL,19,FBetween 2006 and 2009 six men were
OL,20,Fjailed for their parts in the events
OL,21,Fleading to PC Beshenivsky's death.
