OL,6,FKhan evaded justice for more than 14
OL,7,Fyears before his arrest in January
OL,8,F2020.
OL,10,FAs well as murder, he was convicted of
OL,11,Ftwo counts of possessing a firearm
OL,12,Fwith intent to endanger life and two
OL,13,Fcounts of having prohibited firearms.
OL,15,FHe had previously pleaded guilty to
OL,16,Frobbery.
