OL,6,FIn a statement , said: "I have little
OL,7,Fto no memory of my mum and growing up
OL,8,FI have had to hear of her friends and
OL,9,Fgamily talking about her and things
OL,10,Fshe liked to do. She went to work that
OL,11,Fday and never came home. I often think
OL,12,Fshe was a hero that day and paid the
OL,13,Fultimate sacrifice.
