OL,6,F"Since that day and throughout my life
OL,7,Fthere has always been a void but as a
OL,8,Fresult of the violence and callous
OL,9,Factions you Piran Ditta Khan and
OL,10,Fassociates you did that day, you
OL,11,Frobbed me of a future with my mum.
OL,12,FEvery birthday it is a reminder of
OL,13,Fthat day. Recently it has been
OL,14,FMother's Day and my friends celebrated
OL,15,Fwith their mums, and sadly I can't do
OL,16,Fthat."
