OL,6,FPaul Beshenivsky, Sharon's husband,
OL,7,Fsaid in a statement in March: "How can
OL,8,FI ever put into words the impact
OL,9,Flosing Sharon has had on me and our
OL,10,Ffamily? The way we lost Sharon was the
OL,11,Fmost brutal and callous way. She
OL,12,Fshould have come home at the end of
OL,13,Fher shift to celebrate our daughter's
OL,14,Ffourth birthday. She never came home
OL,15,Fbecause of the actions of Piran Ditta
OL,16,FKhan.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/15
