OL,6,F"If Piran Ditta Khan had not organised
OL,7,Fthe robbery, Sharon would not have
OL,8,Fbeen shot dead. She was doing her duty
OL,9,Fas a police officer, a job she loved
OL,10,Fto do, and we are all very proud of
OL,11,Fher. The grief and upset we all
OL,12,Fsuffered is unimaginable but we all
OL,13,Fhad to try and continue."
OL,15,F'We once again pick up the pieces'
