OL,6,FIn a statement given by police outside
OL,7,Fcourt, PC Beshenivsky's family said:
OL,8,F"November 2005 was the start of an
OL,9,Falmost 19-year journey. A journey
OL,10,Fseeking the truth and justice for
OL,11,FSharon, who was not just a police
OL,12,Fofficer, but a loving mum, wife,
OL,13,Fdaughter, sister, and a friend to many.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/15
