OL,6,F"Our journey seeking justice and
OL,7,Fclosure of the judicial process is now
OL,8,Fat an end. This journey has and
OL,9,Fcontinues to be difficult for us all.
OL,10,FEnduring several trials over the years
OL,11,Fhas been hard, each one of them taking
OL,12,Fus back to the very beginning, which
OL,13,Fmade us feel like we had lost Sharon
OL,14,Fall over again. And now we once again
OL,15,Fpick up the pieces of our lives and
OL,16,Fcontinue forward as Sharon would have
OL,17,Fwanted us all to do."
