OL,6,FAssistant Chief Constable Patrick
OL,7,FTwiggs, of West Yorkshire Police,
OL,8,Fsaid: "This is a day of mixed
OL,9,Femotions. On the one hand we are
OL,10,Fpleased to get the final conviction in
OL,11,Fthis case, but on the other hand we
OL,12,Fare sad as it has brought into sharp
OL,13,Ffocus the completely unnecessary waste
OL,14,Fof life that day.
OL,16,F"For 18 years we have never given up
OL,17,Fon getting justice for Sharon and
OL,18,FTeresa, and today their families have
OL,19,Freceived that justice.
