OL,6,F"Sharon was murdered in the line of
OL,7,Fduty, in what was a totally
OL,8,Funnecessary act. Sharon was doing her
OL,9,Fjob and protecting the public.
OL,11,F"The pain and anguish of what happened
OL,12,Fon that day and the profound sense of
OL,13,Floss, will come flooding back to her
OL,14,Ffamily, friends, Police and the local
OL,15,Fcommunity. It was a day we will never
OL,16,Fforget.
OL,18,F"West Yorkshire Police will continue
OL,19,Fto honour Sharon's memory, we still
OL,20,Fmourn the loss, we still miss her, she
OL,21,Fwill be forever in our thoughts."
